{"履修期": "春学期", "主な教授言語": "英語", "授業目的": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:;\">This\ncourse is more advanced than English Communication A/B/C/D. Students should\nhave already completed Contemporary Topics 1. The objectives of this course\nare:</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:;\">1.\nTo develop students’ English proficiency through the study of academic topics\nin the field of sociology.</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:;\">2.\nTo build students’ confidence in using English as a communicative tool.</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:;\">3.\nTo help students improve their listening and note-taking skills through\nextensive lecture-listening activities. </span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:;\">4.\nTo introduce students to significant vocabulary words relevant to a wide range\nof academic topics. </span></p>\n\n<span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\"ｍｓ=\"roman',serif;mso-fareast-font-family:'ｍｓ\" 明朝\";mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-ansi-language:en-us;mso-fareast-language:ja;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa;\"=\"明朝';mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-ansi-language:en-us;mso-fareast-language:ja;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa;'\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:;\">5. To\nprepare students to actively take part in discussions, teaching them the\nfundamental skills for agreeing and disagreeing with others’ opinions.</span>", "到達目標": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:;\">1.\nStudents will develop their academic skills. </span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:;\">2.\nStudents will become more confident and effective communicators.</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:;\">3.\nStudents will strengthen their listening comprehension, note-taking and\ndiscussion skills.</span></p>\n\n<span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\"ｍｓ=\"roman',serif;mso-fareast-font-family:'ｍｓ\" 明朝\";mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-ansi-language:en-us;mso-fareast-language:ja;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa;\"=\"明朝';mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-ansi-language:en-us;mso-fareast-language:ja;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa;'\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:;\">4.\nStudents will acquire new vocabulary that will enhance their academic\nachievement.</span>", "特記事項": "", "関連科目": "<span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\"ｍｓ=\"roman',serif;mso-fareast-font-family:'ｍｓ\" 明朝\";mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-ansi-language:en-us;mso-fareast-language:ja;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa;\"=\"明朝';mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-ansi-language:en-us;mso-fareast-language:ja;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa;'\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:;\">English Communication Advanced D (01-09)</span>", "授業の概要・背景": "", "授業方法": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"roman',serif;mso-fareast-font-family:'times\" roman\";\"=\"roman';'\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:;\">1. This course will be conducte